item.description: What: Jeeves & Wooster in “Perfect Nonsense” Where: Duke of York’s Theatre, Leicester Square, WC2 When: Until 8th March 2014 Price: £15 - £80 As proved by the BBC’s recent TV adaptation of Wodehouse’s Blandings Castle books, which any Wodehouse fan would have found painful to watch, it seems to …
